summary: This is a small collection of books I gathered including my own.
descriptionHtml:
This is a collection of the Magic the Gathering books including the four tomes of the Brothers War . There is also a book, I have written myself. You can find and buy this books by Urag gro shubb at the College of Winterhold. Please give me a feedback on how you liked it.

Hope you enjoy!

Booklist:

The endless journey
The Brothers War
Planeswalker
Time streams
Bloodlines
author: White Crow
